{"data":[{"date":"11:27 07/08","title":"\"Cristiano Ronaldo s\u1ebd kh\u00f4i ph\u1ee5c l\u1ea1i th\u1eddi k\u1ef3 ho\u00e0ng kim c\u1ee7a Serie A\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/2/ronaldo-nhan-xet-cristiano-ronaldo-den-serie-a.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ronaldo Nazario nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u1ebfn Serie A s\u1ebd gi\u00fap gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4i ph\u1ee5c l\u1ea1i th\u1eddi ho\u00e0ng kim c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng n\u0103m \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf k\u1ef7.</h2><h2>Cristiano Ronaldo s\u1ebd kh\u00f4i ph\u1ee5c s\u1ef1 huy ho\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a Serie A<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb sau khi Cristiano Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus, l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin n\u00f3i ri\u00eang v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Serie A c\u0169ng t\u0103ng v\u1ecdt. Ngay \u0111\u1ebfn Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Napoli, Aurelio De Laurentiis c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Ronaldo t\u1ed1t cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u1ebfn Serie A h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ronaldo nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u1ebfn Serie A h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/ronaldo-nhan-xet-cristiano-ronaldo-den-serie-a.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Ronaldo nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u1ebfn Serie A s\u1ebd gi\u00fap gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4i ph\u1ee5c l\u1ea1i th\u1eddi ho\u00e0ng kim.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nRonaldo Nazario t\u1eebng kho\u00e1c \u00e1o c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Milan \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m Serie A v\u1eabn c\u00f2n l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 s\u1ee9c h\u00fat l\u1edbn v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi l\u00fac \u0111\u00f3 nh\u01b0 Zinedine Zidane hay Pavel Nedved. Ronaldo \"b\u00e9o\" tin r\u1eb1ng Cristiano Ronaldo s\u1ebd gi\u00fap kh\u00f4i ph\u1ee5c s\u1ef1 ho\u00e0ng kim ng\u00e0y n\u00e0o c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"S\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi b\u1edfi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ee9c h\u00fat, b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng n\u00e0y s\u1ebd t\u00e1i hi\u1ec7n l\u1ea1i \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3\" - Ronaldo nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t: \"Gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ea7n ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i l\u1ea1i t\u1eeb ho\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t mong \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea5y th\u1eddi k\u1ef3 huy ho\u00e0ng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Inter Milan c\u00f3 ti\u1ebfp b\u01b0\u1edbc Juventus<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau Cris Ronaldo, m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Real Madrid kh\u00e1c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn Serie A l\u00e0 Luka Modric. Inter Milan v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 h\u1eadu thu\u1eabn c\u1ee7a gi\u1edbi ch\u1ee7 Trung Qu\u1ed1c \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 hay nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018 v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Giuseppe Meazza l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ed1i tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi Juventus.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ronaldo Nazario nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y: \"K\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 n\u00e0y th\u1eadt k\u1ef3 l\u1ea1, h\u00e3y xem chuy\u1ec7n g\u00ec s\u1ebd x\u1ea3y ra. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng trong m\u00f9a n\u00e0y, Inter Milan c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec1 ra. C\u00f2n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Modric \u1edf m\u1ed9t kh\u00eda c\u1ea1nh kh\u00e1c, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng gi\u1eefa hai c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9 hay kh\u00f4ng\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"Th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda trong v\u00e0i tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi n\u00ean ch\u00fang ta c\u1ee9 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i th\u00f4i. To\u00e0n b\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111ang b\u1ed5 sung s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 Inter Milan c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ngo\u1ea1i l\u1ec7\".</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 Serie A m\u00f9a 2018-19:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/muc-luong-cua-cristiano-ronaldo-o-juventus-khung-khiep-den-the-nao-176-193834.html\">M\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo \u1edf Juventus kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1ebf n\u00e0o?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/milinkovicsavic-phat-bieu-ve-tuong-lai-176-193781.html\">Sao 120 tri\u1ec7u Euro n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c M.U v\u00e0 Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/inter-quyet-tam-chieu-mo-bang-duoc-luka-modric-176-193748.html\">Inter quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Luka Modric</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/ancelotti-bo-hop-bao-sau-tham-bai-truoc-liverpool-176-193747.html\">Ancelotti b\u1ecf h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o sau th\u1ea3m b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Liverpool</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/leonardo-bonucci-khong-xin-loi-sau-khi-tro-lai-juventus-176-193737.html\">Leonardo Bonucci quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng xin l\u1ed7i sau khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Juventus</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/gattuso-chang-cau-thu-nao-co-the-tu-choi-chung-toi-176-193717.html\">Gattuso: Ch\u1eb3ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i ch\u00fang t\u00f4i</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5190","checkdouble":"193919"},{"date":"10:10 07/08","title":"Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i b\u00e1c b\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Arsenal chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng sao Barca","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/24/huyen-thoai-danh-gia-kha-nang-arsenal-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-dembele.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Martin Keown t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 bi quan v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Arsenal chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb Ousmane Dembele t\u1eeb Barcelona h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>Arsenal nh\u1eafm Dembele</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n t\u1eeb truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha cho th\u1ea5y <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/3-dai-gia-chau-au-dai-chien-vi-qua-bom-xit-cua-barca-180-187555.html\" target=\"_blank\">Arsenal \u0111ang c\u00f3 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb Ousmane Dembele</span> c\u1ee7a Barca.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCho \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac n\u00e0y, HLV Unai Emery \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. C\u00f3 v\u1ebb t\u00e2n thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Keown \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Arsenal chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Dembele h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Keown \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Arsenal chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Dembele h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/huyen-thoai-danh-gia-kha-nang-arsenal-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-dembele.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Keown \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Arsenal chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Dembele</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Martin Keown c\u0169ng m\u1edbi l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 Arsenal c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Dembele l\u00fac n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Dembele ch\u1ec9 t\u1ed1t cho c\u00e1c C\u0110V. C\u00f2n t\u00f4i th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e0y s\u1ebd x\u1ea3y ra. \u0110\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Dembele c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 l\u1edbn. V\u00e0 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 Arsenal chi ra s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n nh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u00fac n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00e1c C\u0110V Arsenal v\u1eabn \u0111ang tr\u00f4ng ch\u1edd v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. Nh\u01b0ng Arsenal m\u1edbi chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Aubameyang h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m v\u00e0 th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ed9t si\u00eau sao kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y\u201d.</em><br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Keown khen ng\u1ee3i Aubameyang</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 chi ra h\u01a1n 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho Aubameyang m\u00f9a \u0111\u00f4ng v\u1eeba qua. V\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Gabon \u0111\u00e3 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Anh. Aubameyang ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 10 b\u00e0n cho Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 ch\u1ec9 sau 14 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i Premier League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cAubameyang s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u00e9 toang h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Premier League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Arsenal s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi b\u1edfi v\u00ec HLV Emery c\u00f3 kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u00e2u h\u01a1n c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ea1nh tranh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cArsenal c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf l\u1edbn khi c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 t\u1eadp trung \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 4 \u0111\u1ebfn 5 tu\u1ea7n. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, nh\u1eefng \u00f4ng l\u1edbn kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh v\u1eabn \u0111ang g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c Arsenal:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-da-tim-duoc-nguoi-thay-the-laurent-koscielny-172-193898.html\">Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Laurent Koscielny?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/ac-milan-khuoc-tu-loi-de-nghi-cua-arsenal-cho-ricardo-rodriguez-184-193914.html\">Arsenal nh\u1eadn tin bu\u1ed3n khi theo \u0111u\u1ed5i sao ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh AC Milan</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5189","checkdouble":"193917"},{"date":"09:39 07/08","title":"Sao Chelsea hy v\u1ecdng Sarri kh\u00f4ng \"kh\u00f3 hi\u1ec3u\" nh\u01b0 Conte","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/30/sao-chelsea-hy-vong-sarri-khong-kho-hieu-nhu-conte.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Willian c\u00f3 d\u1ecbp chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c d\u01b0\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbng HLV Antonio Conte tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u00f4ng b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i v\u00e0 nh\u01b0\u1eddng gh\u1ebf cho \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Maurizio Sarri m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng Sarri kh\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 Conte, ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u00e0 t\u00f4i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 kh\u00f3 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c c\u00f9ng. Tri\u1ebft l\u00fd b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 hay logic c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng \u1ea5y v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p. M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn t\u00f4i ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i l\u1ea1i b\u1ecb thay ra s\u00e2n gi\u1eefa ch\u1eebng. Th\u1eadt kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u n\u1ed5i con ng\u01b0\u1eddi Conte lu\u00f4n!\u201d</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Willian c\u1ee7a Chelsea so s\u00e1nh Conte vs Sarri h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Willian c\u1ee7a Chelsea so s\u00e1nh Conte vs Sarri h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/30/sao-chelsea-hy-vong-sarri-khong-kho-hieu-nhu-conte.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Willian c\u1ee7a Chelsea so s\u00e1nh Conte vs Sarri</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Chuy\u1ec7n Antonio Conte v\u00e0 Willian kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u01b0a th\u00edch nhau v\u1ed1n c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec m\u1edbi l\u1ea1 qua hai n\u0103m tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dd \u1edf Stamford Bridge. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil hi\u1ebfm khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng, \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i kh\u00f4ng \u00edt l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng r\u1eddi Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ee9u v\u00e3n s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p \u1edf m\u1ed9t b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 kh\u00e1c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tuy nhi\u00ean gi\u1edd v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Maurizio Sarri thay th\u1ebf ti\u1ec1n nhi\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng, Willian c\u0169ng t\u1ef1 kh\u1eafc c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 l\u00fd do g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 ra \u0111i n\u1eefa v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ea1nh tranh su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh. Anh n\u00f3i th\u00eam v\u00e0 qua \u0111\u00e2y b\u00e1o tin bu\u1ed3n cho Man Utd c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y c\u0169 Jose Mourinho:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Chelsea v\u00e0 ch\u1eb3ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111i \u0111\u00e2u h\u1ebft c\u1ea3, tr\u1eeb khi CLB mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n t\u00f4i. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 Barcelona g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb nh\u01b0ng gi\u1edd, t\u00f4i to\u00e0n t\u00e2m to\u00e0n \u00fd cho Chelsea. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang r\u1ea5t m\u1edbi m\u1ebb \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi \u2013 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, HLV m\u1edbi, tri\u1ebft l\u00fd m\u1edbi, m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u m\u1edbi.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Willian kh\u00f4ng ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Chelsea tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City \u1edf tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau C\u00fap Anh 2018. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong chuy\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn Huddersfield Town khai m\u1ea1c Premier League 2018/19 cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/willian-nhan-mourinho-toi-muon-lam-viec-voi-ong-mot-lan-nua-nhung-khong-phai-bay-gio-172-193889.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2016/5/28/Willian-tu-choi-kheo-loi-moi-toi-MU-cua-thay-cu-Mourinho-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/willian-nhan-mourinho-toi-muon-lam-viec-voi-ong-mot-lan-nua-nhung-khong-phai-bay-gio-172-193889.html\">Willian mu\u1ed1n t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 Mourinho nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i b\u00e2y gi\u1edd</span><br>\r\nWillian n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gia nh\u1eadp MU khi ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao HLV Jose Mourinho nh\u01b0ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u01b0u ti\u00ean \u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5188","checkdouble":"193918"},{"date":"10:31 07/08","title":"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ea5t b\u00e1t, Pochettino v\u1eabn \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/pochettino-dat-muc-tieu-khong-tuong-cho-tottenham.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Pochettino kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh mong mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u c\u00f9ng Tottenham v\u00e0 ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t tham d\u1ef1 Champions League h\u00e0ng n\u0103m.</h2><h2>Tottenham chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ea5t b\u00e1t\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Pochettino \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng cho Tottenham m\u00f9a 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Pochettino \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng cho Tottenham m\u00f9a 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/pochettino-dat-muc-tieu-khong-tuong-cho-tottenham.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>HLV\u00a0Pochettino \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng cho Tottenham tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Spurs \u0111\u00e3 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch \u1edf nh\u1eefng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 2 ho\u1eb7c th\u1ee9 3 trong 3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. V\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111ang quen d\u1ea7n v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u00e2u \u00c2u l\u00e0 Champions League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Pochettino \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u00c1 qu\u00e2n \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2016/17. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Spurs c\u0169ng \u0111u\u1ed5i kh\u00e1 s\u00e1t Leicester trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u0111\u1ea7y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u1edf m\u00f9a 2015/16 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi h\u1ee5t h\u01a1i \u1edf nh\u1eefng v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ngo\u00e0i mong \u0111\u1ee3i nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi v\u1eabn \u0111ang ph\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7y l\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. L\u00fac n\u00e0y, Tottenham \u0111ang c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng th\u1ea5t b\u00e1t khi l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng duy nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Premier League ch\u01b0a k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u tin \u0111\u1ed3n cho th\u1ea5y Spurs c\u00f3 theo \u0111u\u1ed5i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jack Grealish c\u1ee7a Aston Villa. Nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u1eabn s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Villa Park m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<h2>Pochettino \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 c\u00f2n \u0111ang r\u1ed1i ren, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/huan-luyen-vien/mauricio-pochettino-27.html\" target=\"_blank\">HLV Pochettino</span> v\u1eabn t\u1ecf ra v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng l\u1ea1c quan. \u00d4ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Tottenham s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau l\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 duy tr\u00ec m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trong top 4.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cN\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i ng\u01b0\u1eddi cho r\u1eb1ng HLV c\u1ee7a Tottenham kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u th\u00ec h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 sai l\u1ea7m. T\u00f4i \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Vi\u1ec7c mong mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00e0 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u hay kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0 hai vi\u1ec7c ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00e1c nhau. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tham d\u1ef1 Champions League 3 n\u0103m li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNh\u01b0ng ch\u1eebng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i thay \u0111\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u1ee9. V\u1edbi t\u00f4i, ch\u1ec9 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o top 4 l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u. Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u l\u00e0m t\u00f4i b\u1eadn t\u00e2m v\u00e0 t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u sau 4 n\u0103m n\u1eafm quy\u1ec1n t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cL\u1ecbch s\u1eed v\u00e0 th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c nhau. L\u00fac n\u00e0y, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c c\u1eadt l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t. V\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd \u1edf b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Tottenham:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/cuc-nong-mu-dat-duoc-thoa-thuan-chieu-mo-trung-ve-khung-172-193891.html\">C\u1ef0C N\u00d3NG: MU \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 trung v\u1ec7 kh\u1ee7ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tottenham-sap-co-tan-binh-voi-gia-18-trieu-bang-172-193870.html\">Tottenham mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Chelsea v\u1ee5 sao Aston Villa</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-sap-bien-harry-kane-dat-gia-nhat-the-gioi-180-193833.html\">Real Madrid s\u1eafp bi\u1ebfn Harry Kane \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5187","checkdouble":"193924"},{"date":"11:33 07/08","title":"Phil Jones h\u1ea1 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u00e0nh su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf MU","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/phil-jones-ha-quyet-tam-gianh-suat-da-chinh-o-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trung v\u1ec7 Phil Jones v\u1eeba l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i Man United, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</h2><h2>MU nh\u1eafm mua trung v\u1ec7</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Man United \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u. Jerome Boateng, Toby Alderweireld, Harry Maguire, Jose Gimenez v\u00e0 Kalidou Koulibaly l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/phil-jones-43834.html\" target=\"_blank\">Phil Jones</span> ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u 25 tr\u1eadn v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Nh\u01b0ng anh \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, Jones c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft FA Cup v\u1edbi Chelsea b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Chris Smalling. M\u00f9a h\u00e8 v\u1eeba qua, Phil Jones c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Southgate g\u1ecdi l\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u0111\u1ec3 tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Phil Jones \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1eaft ng\u1eafn k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 h\u00e8 \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. Anh c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong hi\u1ec7p hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Bayern Munich h\u00f4m Ch\u1ee7 nh\u1eadt v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Jones h\u1ea1 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u00e0nh su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Trung v\u1ec7 Phil Jones h\u1ea1 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u00e0nh su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Trung v\u1ec7 Phil Jones h\u1ea1 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u00e0nh su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/phil-jones-ha-quyet-tam-gianh-suat-da-chinh-o-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Phil Jones h\u1ea1 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u00e0nh su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00f3, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi Maguire, Alderweireld, Boateng hay b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Man United trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cLu\u00f4n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n Man United mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u00e1c trung v\u1ec7 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. V\u00e0 t\u00f4i c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n r\u1eb1ng Man United s\u1ebd lu\u00f4n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi n\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn trong \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. B\u1ea1n lu\u00f4n bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh ph\u1ea3i ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t th\u00ec m\u1edbi c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n. V\u00e0 khi b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u00ec b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c su\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ch\u00ednh\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Man United:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-giai-thich-ly-do-marcus-rashford-mang-ao-so-10-cua-man-utd-172-193910.html\">Mourinho gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch l\u00fd do Marcus Rashford mang \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 c\u1ee7a Man Utd</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-0708-them-mot-cau-thu-chinh-thuc-chia-tay-mu-184-193907.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 07/08: Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C chia tay MU</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5186","checkdouble":"193930"},{"date":"11:27 07/08","title":"Quan \u0111i\u1ec3m: M.U n\u00ean g\u1ea1t b\u1ecf s\u0129 di\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 mua l\u1ea1i Wilfried Zaha","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/7/quan-diem-mu-nen-mua-zaha.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, Wilfried Zaha t\u1eebng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i th\u1ea3m h\u1ea1i trong cu\u1ed9c phi\u00eau l\u01b0u t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Old Trafford. Tuy nhi\u00ean, t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i h\u01a1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0 M.U n\u00ean mua Zaha \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ee9c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng b\u00ean c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Zaha \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean m\u1ed9t t\u1ea7m cao m\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sir Alex Ferguson l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u Man United chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Wilfried Zaha t\u1eeb Crystal Palace \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2013. Tuy nhi\u00ean, HLV v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf l\u1ea1i ch\u01b0a m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc cho Zaha v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 M.U.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a 2013/14 d\u01b0\u1edbi tay \u201cNg\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ecdn\u201d David Moyes, Zaha kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng kh\u00f4ng ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 m\u00e0 c\u00f2n \u0111i th\u1ee5t l\u00f9i. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh nhanh nh\u01b0 s\u00f3c n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n 4 l\u1ea7n tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u1ecb \u0111em cho Cardiff City m\u01b0\u1ee3n. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Quan \u0111i\u1ec3m MU n\u00ean mua Zaha \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Quan \u0111i\u1ec3m MU n\u00ean mua Zaha \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/quan-diem-mu-nen-mua-zaha.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Zaha t\u1eebng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf Man United</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n7 th\u00e1ng sau, M.U ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn ch\u1ecbu l\u1ed7 b\u00e1n th\u00e1o Zaha cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 Crystal Palace. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u1edd v\u1eabn c\u00f2n \u00e1m \u1ea3nh ch\u00e0ng trai 25 tu\u1ed5i. Nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y t\u0103m t\u1ed1i t\u1ea1i th\u00e0nh Manchester l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c cho Zaha v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n4 m\u00f9a qua, Zaha ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t hay t\u1ea1i CLB \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o m\u00ecnh. \u0110\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, t\u1eeb Chelsea, Liverpool t\u1edbi Tottenham \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 mang 2 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ecbch B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0 v\u00e0 Anh. H\u1ecd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng tr\u1ea3 m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 l\u00ean t\u1edbi 75 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho Crystal Palace \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Zaha.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-nang-gia-hoi-mua-hang-thai-mu-len-75-trieu-bang-172-193773.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/5/chelsea-nang-gia-hoi-mua-hang-thai-mu-len-75-trieu-bang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-nang-gia-hoi-mua-hang-thai-mu-len-75-trieu-bang-172-193773.html\">Chelsea n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua \u201ch\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i\u201d MU l\u00ean 75 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</span><br>\r\n<span>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Wilfried Zaha thay Willian, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 75 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 n\u00f3i l\u00ean \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a Zaha. M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, ch\u1ec9 Eden Hazard c\u1ee7a Chelsea c\u00f3 s\u1ed1 pha qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi trung b\u00ecnh m\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh th\u00e1ng 11 n\u0103m 1995. T\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng, anh c\u00f3 9 b\u00e0n, 3 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eb9, g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n \u201cc\u1ee9u s\u1ed1ng\u201d Palace tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng sau kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ebft b\u00e1t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi Zaha \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i t\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft. Gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n tin r\u1eb1ng M.U n\u00ean mua Zaha \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 s\u1ee9c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u00e1nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Zaha toa sang tai Palace\" title=\"Zaha toa sang tai Palace\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/Zaha-toa-sang-tai-Palace.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Zaha \u0111\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi 5 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nM.U c\u1ea7n t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p Zaha</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ef1 th\u1ef1c th\u00ec ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Man United nghi\u00eam t\u00fac \u0111\u01b0a Wilfried Zaha tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i. H\u1ecd \u0111ang qu\u00e1 t\u1eadp trung cho vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ivan Perisic hay Willian. Tuy nhi\u00ean, M.U v\u1ea5p ph\u1ea3i s\u1ef1 c\u1ee9ng r\u1eafn t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Inter Milan v\u00e0 Chelsea. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u1ea3n th\u00e2n nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 kh\u00e1t khao chuy\u1ec3n b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7. M\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, Willian nh\u1eafn Jose Mourinho: \u201cT\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi \u00f4ng m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i b\u00e2y gi\u1edd\u201d. Nh\u01b0ng Zaha th\u00ec kh\u00e1c. M\u1ed9t Crystal Palace ch\u1ec9 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng kh\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn anh c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y th\u1ecfa m\u00e3n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/zaha-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-172-192254.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/13/zaha-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/zaha-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-172-192254.html\">M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng b\u00e1o tin vui cho Tottenham v\u00e0 Chelsea</span><br>\r\n<span>Wilfried Zaha n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Crystal Palace \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nZaha c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac t\u00ecm m\u1ed9t b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 gi\u00e0u tham v\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ecfa s\u1ee9c v\u1eaby v\u00f9ng. N\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd, anh s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec7 \u0111\u01a1n xin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Th\u1eadt l\u1ea1 khi l\u00fac n\u00e0y M.U ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Palace v\u00e0 Zaha.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u M.U s\u1ee3 \u0111i\u1ec1u ti\u1ebfng. 4 n\u0103m sau khi \u0111\u1ea9y Zaha tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Palace v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 ch\u1ec9 6 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd chi \u0111\u1eadm 75 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua l\u1ea1i anh \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng khai th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 sai l\u1ea7m. S\u1ebd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ef1u Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf nh\u01b0 Moyes s\u1ebd b\u1ecb \u0111em ra \u201cm\u1ed5 x\u1ebb\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"PCT Ed Woodward cua Man United\" title=\"PCT Ed Woodward c\u1ee7a Man United\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/7/9/Buoc-tien-cua-Quy-do-Su-doi-moi-trong-cach-thuc-mua-nguoi-hinh-anh-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">L\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a M.U ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Palace</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng? \u0110\u1eebng qu\u00ean r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 2 n\u0103m, ch\u00ednh M.U \u0111\u00e3 chi kho\u1ea3n ph\u00ed k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi khi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 89 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Paul Pogba, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ea9y \u0111i d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do v\u00e0i m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed9t k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u00fat ra: M\u1ed9t khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u01b0 Mourinho \u01b0a th\u00edch, c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n s\u1eeda ch\u1eefa sai l\u1ea7m kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i qu\u00e1 to t\u00e1t. 75 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n nh\u1ecf, nh\u01b0ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng CLB kh\u00e1c. M.U v\u1eabn gi\u00e0u c\u00f3 nh\u1ea5t nh\u00ec th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ch\u1ec9 n\u1eb1m \u1edf ng\u1ea1i ng\u00f9ng hay kh\u00f4ng m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Zaha hoan thien minh\" title=\"Zaha hoan thien minh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/Zaha-hoan-thien-minh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Nh\u01b0ng M.U n\u00ean mua Zaha \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a Zaha l\u00e0 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i v\u00e0 d\u1ea1t v\u00e0o trung l\u1ed9. Tuy nhi\u00ean, anh v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i th\u00e0nh th\u1ea1o b\u00ean c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i. D\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Roy Hodgson, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p di chuy\u1ec3n t\u1ef1 do, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u1edf m\u1ecdi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00f3ng anh c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y s\u00e1t th\u01b0\u01a1ng cho khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ef1c ra, t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Zaha \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u1eeb 7 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi m\u1edbi 18, 19 tu\u1ed5i. Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i M.U t\u1edbi t\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh t\u1ea1i Abidjan, B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Nga thi\u1ebfu \u0111i b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh v\u00e0 kinh nghi\u1ec7m tr\u1eadn m\u1ea1c. Th\u1eddi gian tr\u00f4i qua, Zaha \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1eefng ch\u1ea1c h\u01a1n v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng th\u1ebf vai Juan Mata ch\u01b0a khi n\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 h\u1ee3p \u00fd Mourinho \u0111\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i M.U.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u0129 nhi\u00ean, khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Old Trafford, Zaha c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i x\u1ed1c v\u00e1c tham gia ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 h\u01a1n (\u0111i\u1ec1u Mata kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng), tr\u00e1i v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 nhi\u1ec1u nh\u01b0 t\u1ea1i Palace. Nh\u01b0ng nh\u00ecn chung, \u0111\u00e2y v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ea3nh gh\u00e9p tr\u00ean l\u00fd thuy\u1ebft l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i m\u00e0 M.U \u0111ang tri\u1ec3n khai.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jose Mourinho dang duong dau voi mua giai ban le tai Man Utd.\" title=\"Jose Mourinho \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i b\u1ea3n l\u1ec1 t\u1ea1i Man Utd.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/nghich-ly-cua-jose-mourinho-dinh-kien-thua-nhan-hay-khong-thua-nhan.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t h\u1ee3p \u00fd Mourinho</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o, Mourinho c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n nh\u1eefng pha t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u1edf hai c\u00e1nh th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, tr\u1ef1c di\u1ec7n. \u00d4ng \u0111ang c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111e d\u1ecda khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, gi\u1ea3m b\u1edbt g\u00e1nh n\u1eb7ng ghi b\u00e0n cho Romelu Lukaku. Zaha c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng h\u1ebft nh\u1eefng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u00fd ki\u1ebfn cho r\u1eb1ng M.U \u0111\u00e3 qu\u00e1 v\u1ed9i v\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i lo\u1ea1i Zaha trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9. 4 n\u0103m qua cho th\u1ea5y \u0111\u00fang l\u00e0 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. Zaha \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng minh nh\u1eefng Moyes hay Van Gaal \u0111\u00e3 m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m l\u1edbn v\u00e0 gi\u1edd Mourinho c\u00f9ng l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u1ea7n s\u1eeda ch\u1eefa gi\u00fap h\u1ecd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem l\u1ea1i m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Wilfried Zaha \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/7/Wilfried-Zaha-201718.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Man United tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/rashford-va-chiec-ao-huyen-thoai-trach-nhiem-nang-ne-kha-nang-han-che-172-193843.html\">Rashford v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i: Tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/quan-diem-andreas-pereira-xung-dang-co-mat-trong-doi-hinh-mu-172-192629.html\">Quan \u0111i\u1ec3m: Sao tr\u1ebb gh\u00e9t b\u1ecb cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c M.U tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-trieu-dai-moi-emery-hoc-hoi-sai-lam-cua-mu-va-liverpool-172-192409.html\">Arsenal tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i m\u1edbi: C\u1ea3m \u01a1n nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m c\u1ee7a MU v\u00e0 Liverpool</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/man-utd-he-2018-jose-mourinho-va-su-phu-phang-voi-nhung-mang-non-172-192408.html\">Jose Mourinho v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 ph\u0169 ph\u00e0ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng m\u0103ng non</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5185","checkdouble":"193931"},{"date":"08:21 07/08","title":"Di\u1ec5n vi\u00ean Vi\u1ec7t Anh \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Dental Cup 2018","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/7/dien-vien-viet-anh-dua-doi-bong-gianh-chuc-vo-dich-giai-dental-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 6/8, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mang t\u00ean Nacera c\u1ee7a di\u1ec5n vi\u00ean Vi\u1ec7t Anh \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch C\u00fap Li\u00ean hi\u1ec7p c\u00e1c nha khoa.</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 phong tr\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean do Li\u00ean Hi\u1ec7p Nha khoa t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c. M\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch c\u1ee7a ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng n\u00e0y l\u00e0 t\u1ea1o c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng Nha khoa c\u00f9ng giao l\u01b0u t\u0103ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 chia s\u1ebb kinh nghi\u1ec7m trong vi\u1ec7c th\u0103m kh\u00e1m, ch\u1eefa tr\u1ecb c\u00e1c b\u1ec7nh v\u1ec1 r\u0103ng mi\u1ec7ng \u1edf Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</p>\r\n<div class=\"imagecontainer\" style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%;\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n            <td align=\"center\" style=\"width: 100%;\"><img alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/Do%CC%A3%CC%82i-bo%CC%81ng-cu%CC%89a-Vie%CC%A3%CC%82t-Anh-1.jpg\" style=\"border: none;\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <p><em>\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nha Khoa Nacera c\u1ee7a nam di\u1ec5n vi\u00ean &ldquo;Ng\u01b0\u1eddi ph\u00e1n x\u1eed&rdquo; trong bu\u1ed5i ra qu\u00e2n</em><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e3 thu h\u00fat \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 tham gia c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb c\u00e1c nha khoa tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ecba b\u00e0n H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 tham gia c\u1ee7a di\u1ec5n vi\u00ean Vi\u1ec7t Anh c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mang t\u00ean Nacera. V\u1edbi th\u1ec3 th\u1ee9c thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng tr\u00f2n t\u00ednh \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1eb1m t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c giao l\u01b0u v\u1edbi nhau.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tham gia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e2n th\u00e0nh c\u00e1c c\u1eb7p thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi nhau, m\u1ed7i \u0111\u1ed9i g\u1ed3m 12 th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng b\u00e1c s\u0129, y t\u00e1 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1m. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh ng\u00f4i v\u1ecb cao nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 &ldquo;Cup v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch&rdquo; , Dental Cup c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i ph\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00edch l\u1ec7 tinh th\u1ea7n c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u01b0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t.</p>\r\n<div class=\"imagecontainer\" style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%;\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n            <td align=\"center\" style=\"width: 100%;\"><img alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/Do%CC%A3%CC%82i-bo%CC%81ng-cu%CC%89a-Vie%CC%A3%CC%82t-Anh-3.jpg\" style=\"border: none;\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <p><em>\u0110\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n nha khoa th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf Nacera, \u00f4ng L\u00ea Huy Th\u00e0nh l\u00ean nh\u1eadn ph\u1ea7n th\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1eeb nh\u00e0 t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3<br>\r\n            </em></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"imagecontainer\" style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%;\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n            <td align=\"center\" style=\"width: 100%;\"><img alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/Do%CC%A3%CC%82i-bo%CC%81ng-cu%CC%89a-Vie%CC%A3%CC%82t-Anh-5.jpg\" style=\"border: none;\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 c\u1ea3m x\u00fac sau khi gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, di\u1ec5n vi\u00ean Vi\u1ec7t Anh cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t b\u1edfi th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n tham gia \u0111a s\u1ed1 l\u00e0 c\u00e1c b\u00e1c s\u0129. Vi\u1ec7t Anh \u0111\u00e3 tham gia nhi\u1ec1u gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng hay c\u1ee7a gi\u1edbi ngh\u1ec7 s\u0129 nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ng\u1edd c\u00e1c b\u00e1c s\u0129 l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e1 b\u00f3ng hay \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. Khi ra s\u00e2n c\u1ecf, c\u00e1c b\u00e1c s\u0129 \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7y nhi\u1ec7t huy\u1ebft, l\u0103n x\u1ea3 h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh theo nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng cho d\u00f9 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 l\u00fac n\u00e0o&rdquo;.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Clip ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n di\u1ec5n vi\u00ean Vi\u1ec7t Anh<br>\r\n</strong></p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/7/Vie\u0323\u0302t-Anh.mp4\" data-width=\"100%\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"https://cms.bongda24h.vn/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 320px;\"></div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1ea3i qua nhi\u1ec1u v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u, Nacera c\u1ee7a di\u1ec5n vi\u00ean Vi\u1ec7t Anh \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Vi\u1ec7t V\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 d\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111u\u1ed5i 4-3. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra g\u00e2y c\u1ea5n, c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft v\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n th\u1ec3 thao fair play. Th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p s\u1ee9c, \u0111\u1ed3ng l\u00f2ng v\u00e0 \u0111o\u00e0n k\u1ebft c\u1ee7a t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean b\u00e1c s\u0129, y t\u00e1 trong t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 Nha Khoa Nacera. D\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf 5 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, di\u1ec5n vi\u00ean Vi\u1ec7t Anh ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u00f4ng qua gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u, BTC mong mu\u1ed1n k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i v\u00e0 \u0111em l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i th\u1ec3 thao cho li\u00ean hi\u1ec7p c\u00e1c nha khoa to\u00e0n mi\u1ec1n B\u1eafc.</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5184","checkdouble":"193913"},{"date":"07:12 07/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Uzbekistan (19h30 ng\u00e0y 07/8): \u0110\u00f2i n\u1ee3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00f4ng?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/nhan-dinh-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-uzbekistan-19h30-ngay-078-doi-no-duoc-khong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i '\u0111\u00f2i n\u1ee3' tr\u01b0\u1edbc U23 Uzbekistan sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018. V\u00e0 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo \u0111ang c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf \u1edf tr\u1eadn t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u01b0u th\u1ebf v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 nh\u00e0, \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00fac n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ch\u1ecbu nh\u1eefng \u00e1p l\u1ef1c thi \u0111\u1ea5u khi \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch sau c\u00e1c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Palestine v\u00e0 Oman.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 khi m\u00e0 m\u1ecdi lo ng\u1ea1i hay \u00e1p l\u1ef1c t\u00e2m l\u00fd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1edfi b\u1ecf, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin cao nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c U23 Uzbekistan, qua \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00f2i l\u1ea1i m\u00f3n n\u1ee3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Uzbekistan (19h30 ng\u00e0y 078) \u0110\u00f2i n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Uzbekistan (19h30 ng\u00e0y 078) \u0110\u00f2i n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/a2-2538-1533521216.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Uzbekistan: \u0110\u00f2i n\u1ee3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00f4ng?</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111ang c\u00f3 trong tay 29 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c sung m\u00e3n, ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a H\u1ed3ng Duy. V\u00e0 r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3, cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c v\u1edbi Uzbeksitan s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u00e0n t\u1ed5ng duy\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o ASIAD 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf th\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng l\u1edbn, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. B\u1edfi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd c\u1ea7n h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf t\u1ed1i \u0111a nh\u1eefng pha va ch\u1ea1m c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1eabn t\u1edbi ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ASIAD. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ed9 h\u1ebft &lsquo;b\u00e0i v\u1edf&rsquo; tr\u01b0\u1edbc con m\u1eaft theo d\u00f5i c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ef1 c\u1ed5 v\u0169, \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a NHM, r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u s\u00f4i \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft l\u00e0m qua d\u00e0nh t\u1eb7ng kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3. Ngo\u00e0i ra, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u0169ng \u0111ang khao kh\u00e1t m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uzbekistan. V\u00ec th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y d\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 mang t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t giao h\u1eefu c\u0169ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00f2i l\u1ea1i m\u00f3n n\u1ee1 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng vay c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Uzbekistan \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm sau tr\u1eadn thua Palestine \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc. V\u00e0 n\u1ebfu thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00fang s\u1ee9c, \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 m\u00ecnh mong mu\u1ed1n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>U23 Uzbekistan kh\u00f3 t\u1ea1o b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Palestine \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y U23 Uzbekistan l\u00fac n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 v\u1eeba l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00ednh HLV c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Trung \u00c1 th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Kh\u00e1c v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1, l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y Uzbekistan l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i y\u1ebfu h\u01a1n. Trong khi Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1eabn gi\u1eef nguy\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ea1i Trung Qu\u1ed1c th\u00ec Uzbekistan ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n hai, ba ng\u01b0\u1eddi. Song l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t HLV, \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n mu\u1ed1n chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ea1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam&rdquo;, HLV Nuraliev Dilshod cho bi\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"U23 Uzbekistan\" title=\"U23 Uzbekistan\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/4/doi-hinh-u23-uzbekistan-sang-viet-nam-khong-chat-luong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>U23 Uzbekistan kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edbi v\u1edbi gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Trung \u00c1 kh\u00f4ng mang theo \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t. Tr\u00e1i v\u1edbi tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1ea3i, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 mang \u0111\u1ebfn Vi\u1ec7t Nam m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 m\u1edbi ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n, v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00fang 4 c\u00e1i t\u00ean t\u1eebng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Trung Qu\u1ed1c h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1edbi c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t HLV c\u0169ng c\u00f2n kh\u00e1 m\u1edbi m\u1ebb, U23 Uzbekistan nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi trong tay HLV Park Hang Seo l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111ang c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m ngo\u00e0i 23 tu\u1ed5i. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1edfi v\u1eady kh\u00f4ng kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u1eefa. K\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 khi kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn v\u1eabn s\u1ebd c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft cho C\u0110V nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sang Indonesia tranh t\u00e0i t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn:</strong><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam:&nbsp;V\u0103n L\u00e2m, V\u0103n Thanh, Duy M\u1ea1nh, Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng,V\u0103n H\u1eadu; Quang H\u1ea3i, H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng, Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft. C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Anh \u0110\u1ee9c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">U23 Uzbekistan:&nbsp;Karimov Sarvar (GK), Ibrokhim, Abdulla, Ilkhomjon, Javokhir, Sherzod, Nurillo, Sardorbek, Farukh, Oybek, Arorbek.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n:&nbsp;U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 3-1 U23 Uzbekistan.</strong></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/van-hau-la-cua-hiem-cua-bong-da-viet-168-193864.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/5/van-hau-la-cua-hiem-cua-bong-da-viet.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/van-hau-la-cua-hiem-cua-bong-da-viet-168-193864.html\">V\u0103n H\u1eadu l\u00e0 c\u1ee7a hi\u1ebfm c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t</span><br>\r\nCh\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn m\u00e0n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0110o\u00e0n V\u0103n H\u1eadu t\u1ea1i U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, HLV CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u00f4ng Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i cho m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/u23-thai-lan-loai-mot-loat-cau-thu-sau-that-bai-tai-myanmar-168-193860.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/4/u23-thai-lan-loai-mot-loat-cau-thu-sau-that-bai-tai-myanmar.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/u23-thai-lan-loai-mot-loat-cau-thu-sau-that-bai-tai-myanmar-168-193860.html\">U23 Th\u00e1i Lan lo\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i Myanmar</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn thua t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i \u1edf gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu Alpine Cup 2018, ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n U23 Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh lo\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ASIAD.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/u23-viet-nam-vo-dich-vinaphone-cup-loi-khang-dinh-cua-thay-park-168-193817.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/u23-viet-nam-vo-dich-vinaphone-cup-loi-khang-dinh-cua-thay-park.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/u23-viet-nam-vo-dich-vinaphone-cup-loi-khang-dinh-cua-thay-park-168-193817.html\">U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf: L\u1eddi kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y Park</span><br>\r\nTh\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u00e0 kinh nghi\u1ec7m trong ngh\u1ec1 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi gi\u00fap  U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Vinaphone Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:11.5pt;font-family:\" new=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5183","checkdouble":"193900"},{"date":"07:23 07/08","title":"Tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ef1u v\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf gi\u1ea3i U16 \u0110N\u00c1, HLV \u0110T U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u00f3i g\u00ec?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/4/tro-thanh-cuu-vuong-o-giai-u16-dna-hlv-dt-u16-viet-nam-noi-gi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1ed9t n\u0103m sau th\u00e0nh t\u00edch v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i U15 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1, ch\u00ednh l\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a HLV V\u0169 H\u1ed3ng Vi\u1ec7t \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u00ea ch\u1ec1 t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i U16 \u0110N\u00c1 2018. V\u00e0 nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y?</h2><h2>HLV V\u0169 H\u1ed3ng Vi\u1ec7t n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi \u0110T U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i?</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ef1u v\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf gi\u1ea3i U16 \u0110N\u00c1, HLV \u0110T U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u00f3i g\u00ec h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ef1u v\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf gi\u1ea3i U16 \u0110N\u00c1, HLV \u0110T U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u00f3i g\u00ec h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/7/22/Tro-thanh-cuu-vuong-o-giai-U16-DNA,-HLV-DT-U16-Viet-Nam-noi-gi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV V\u0169 H\u1ed3ng Vi\u1ec7t kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc U16 Myanmar</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y 6/8, U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 2-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Myanmar. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i so thua k\u00e9m ch\u00ednh Myanmar v\u1ec1 ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 ph\u1ee5.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, HLV V\u0169 H\u1ed3ng Vi\u1ec7t \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ea5u n\u1ed5i s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt v\u1ecdng v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2. \u00d4ng cho bi\u1ebft: &quot;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u01b0\u1edbi m\u1ee9c trung b\u00ecnh. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">To\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn v\u1edbi \u00e1p l\u1ef1c cao nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. R\u1ea5t ti\u1ebfc khi U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn s\u00e2u \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u1edf gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay.&quot;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n, HLV Myanmar \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 l\u1eddi khen x\u00e3 giao cho c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 HLV V\u0169 H\u1ed3ng Vi\u1ec7t. V\u1ecb n\u00e0y nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t: &quot;U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd tuy nhi\u00ean trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 th\u00eam may m\u1eafn n\u1eefa. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 v\u00e0 t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft.&quot;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0110N\u00c1, \u0110T U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i U16 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 t\u1ea1i Malaysia v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m nay.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/u16-viet-nam-vs-u16-myanmar-ngay-hom-nay-68-372-193846.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/u16-viet-nam-vs-u16-myanmar-ngay-hom-nay-68.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/u16-viet-nam-vs-u16-myanmar-ngay-hom-nay-68-372-193846.html\">U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 2-2 U16 Myanmar (KT): U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ef1u v\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1</span><br>\r\nB\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch U16 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018 g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ea1nh tranh tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U16 Myanmar v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n v\u00e0o b\u00e1n...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><br>\r\nVideo: U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 2-2 U16 Myanmar<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">\t</span></strong></p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/6/U16-Viet-Nam-2-2-U16-Myanmar.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;&#10;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5182","checkdouble":"193905"},{"date":"08:04 07/08","title":"HLV Uzbekistan n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5u U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/4/hlv-uzbekistan-noi-gi-truoc-tran-tai-dau-u23-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, HLV Nuraliev Dilshod c\u1ee7a Uzbekistan th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00e1p \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo.</h2><h2>HLV Uzbekistan \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u00f3 v\u1edbi \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam?</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018, \u0110T U23 Uzbekistan l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao \u1edf gi\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed tr\u1eadn t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Uzbekistan c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c BTC gi\u1ea3i kh\u00e9o l\u00e9o s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 t\u00e1i hi\u1ec7n l\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Song tr\u00e1i v\u1edbi d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n c\u1ee7a BTC v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9, \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0110T U23 Uzbekistan sang Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y l\u1ea1i bao g\u1ed3m nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t tr\u1ebb, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u0103m nay m\u1edbi 19 tu\u1ed5i. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn U23 Uzbekistan b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV U23 Uzbekistan n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5u U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV U23 Uzbekistan n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5u U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/4/thua-palestine-hlv-u23-uzbekistan-thua-nhan-thua-kem-u23-viet-nam.jpg\"><br>\r\n            <em>HLV U23 Uzbekistan \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u00f3 v\u1edbi \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam?</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: right;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: right;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, xem l\u1ea1i c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, HLV Uzbekistan c\u00f3 v\u1ebb nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 r\u00fat ra kinh nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u00f3 v\u1edbi Vi\u1ec7t Nam. V\u1ecb n\u00e0y n\u00f3i: &ldquo;N\u1ebfu c\u1ee9 \u0111\u00e1 nh\u01b0 n\u00e0y th\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng m\u00e0 th\u1eafng n\u1ed5i U.23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, th\u1ebf n\u00ean t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i d\u1eb7n d\u00f2 k\u1ef9 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. B\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e1c xa c\u00e1i ng\u00e0y m\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i m\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ebfn 120 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong d\u00e1nh s\u00e1ch 20 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 HLV Nuraliev Dilshod mang sang Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i T\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 4 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng tham d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng U.23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1, c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t r\u1ea5t tr\u1ebb. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n m\u00e0 HLV Nuraliev cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a U23 Uzbekistan \u1edf gi\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;L\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng U.23 Uzbekistan sang \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e1 giao h\u1eefu l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t d\u00e0n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t tr\u1ebb v\u00e0 thi\u1ebfu kinh nghi\u1ec7m. N\u1ebfu so v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t t\u1edbi tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U.23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u1ea1i \u0111ang \u1edf \u0111\u1ec9nh cao phong \u0111\u1ed9, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi nhau t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t l\u00e2u r\u1ed3i, v\u00e0 t\u00f4i c\u0169ng bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi nhau \u1edf gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG n\u00ean r\u1ea5t hi\u1ec3u nhau, t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft r\u00f5 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y v\u00e0 s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00e1p h\u1ee3p l\u00fd cho tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i&rdquo;, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n U.23 Uzbekistan t\u00e2m s\u1ef1.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Uzbekistan s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 19g30 ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 7/8. Sau khi k\u1ebft th\u00fac gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu n\u00e0y, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd di chuy\u1ec3n v\u00e0o B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n cho \u0111\u1ebfn khi l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 18.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-uzbekistan-19h30-ngay-078-doi-no-duoc-khong-168-193900.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/nhan-dinh-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-uzbekistan-19h30-ngay-078-doi-no-duoc-khong.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-uzbekistan-19h30-ngay-078-doi-no-duoc-khong-168-193900.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Uzbekistan (19h30 ng\u00e0y 07/8): \u0110\u00f2i n\u1ee3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00f4ng?</span><br>\r\nU23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00f2i n\u1ee3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc U23 Uzbekistan sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018. V\u00e0 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo \u0111ang c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf \u1edf...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-le-thuy-hai-chi-ra-han-che-cua-u23-viet-nam-168-193797.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/10/29/hlv-le-thuy-hai-chi-ra-han-che-cua-u23-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-le-thuy-hai-chi-ra-han-che-cua-u23-viet-nam-168-193797.html\">HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i ch\u1ec9 ra h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nCh\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i kh\u00f3 nh\u1ecdc c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc Oman, \u00f4ng L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t th\u1eb3ng th\u1eafn v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-phan-thanh-hung-noi-gi-ve-man-trinh-dien-cua-u23-viet-nam-168-193807.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/9/hlv-phan-thanh-hung-noi-gi-ve-man-trinh-dien-cua-u23-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-phan-thanh-hung-noi-gi-ve-man-trinh-dien-cua-u23-viet-nam-168-193807.html\">HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam?</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Roboto;mso-fareast-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5181","checkdouble":"193911"},{"date":"07:18 07/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Liverpool vs Torino 01h30 ng\u00e0y 8/8 (Giao h\u1eefu CLB h\u00e8 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/5/nhan-dinh-liverpool-vs-torino-01h30-ngay-88-giao-huu-clb-he-2018.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Liverpool vs Torino l\u00fac 01h30 ng\u00e0y 8/8 (Giao h\u1eefu CLB h\u00e8 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: start; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> Liverpool vs Torino: 4-1<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\nTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i th\u1eafng Napoli 5-0 \u0111\u00eam th\u1ee9 B\u1ea3y v\u1eeba qua m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa x\u00e1c quy\u1ebft \u01b0u th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a Liverpool tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia. Nay \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Anfield, The Kop s\u1ebd c\u00e0ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 \u201cb\u1eaft n\u1ea1t\u201d \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Serie A.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Liverpool vs Torino 01h30 ng\u00e0y 88 Giao h\u1eefu CLB h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Liverpool vs Torino 01h30 ng\u00e0y 88 Giao h\u1eefu CLB h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/5/video-tong-hop-liverpool-50-napoli-giao-huu-clb-he-2018.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nLiverpool \u0111ang c\u00f3 chu\u1ed7i 3 tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ef1c m\u1ea1nh. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Napoli h\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua c\u1ea3 2 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Manchester. HLV Juergen Klopp \u0111ang bu\u1ed9c c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t nghi\u00eam t\u00fac trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nLiverpool \u0111\u00e3 ghi c\u1ea3 th\u1ea3y 24 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 8 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u H\u00e8 2018 t\u1edbi nay, t\u1ee9c trung b\u00ecnh m\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn The Kop n\u00e3 v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 3 l\u1ea7n. Phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Mohamed Salah v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i khi\u1ebfn m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 khi\u1ebfp s\u1ee3, ch\u1ee9 ch\u01b0a n\u00f3i \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t Torino c\u00f3 t\u1ea7m v\u00f3c khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTorino th\u1eafng 4 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0 lu\u00f4n s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ea7u h\u1ebft l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u00f4 danh. Tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Anfield n\u01a1i m\u00e0 m\u1ecdi CLB \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u01b0 Juventus, Milan, Inter v\u00e0 Roma \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1eebng nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3, Torino kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u1eeda g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i \u00e1 qu\u00e2n Champions League. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1eb6C BI\u1ec6T<br>\r\n3 b\u00e0n tr\u1edf l\u00ean<br>\r\n5/7 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a Torino v\u00e0 8/10 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Liverpool \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 3 b\u00e0n tr\u1edf l\u00ean. V\u1edbi s\u1ee9c c\u00f4ng ph\u00e1 \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3 c\u1ee7a Liverpool, nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh cu\u1ed9c so t\u00e0i \u0111\u00eam nay s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u01b0a g\u00f4n. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Bongdaplus.vn<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5180","checkdouble":"193902"},{"date":"07:43 07/08","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 07/08: Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C chia tay MU","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/1/26/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-0708-them-mot-cau-thu-chinh-thuc-chia-tay-mu.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 07/08.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C chia tay MU</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 0708 Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 chia tay MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 0708 Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 chia tay MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/26/tua.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Tuanzebe c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Aston Villa theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nTheo th\u00f4ng tin ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i, trung v\u1ec7 Axel Tuanzebe r\u1eddi M.U t\u1edbi Aston Villa theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 1 n\u0103m, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y m\u1edf ra kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf b\u1ed5 sung \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Barca g\u1eedi MU: 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng + Mina + Andre Gomes = Pogba?</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Paul Pogba c\u1ee7a M.U, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u1ed9ng trung v\u1ec7 Mina v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m Andre Gomes \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>David Luiz: &ldquo;Courtois v\u00e0 Hazard c\u1ee9 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i ra \u0111i&rdquo;</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, trung v\u1ec7 David Luiz chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Courtois v\u00e0 Hazard \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, r\u1eb1ng b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Kroos: &ldquo;Qu\u00e1 kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf Ronaldo&rdquo;</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Toni Kroos ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Ronaldo v\u00e0 cho r\u1eb1ng, Real Madrid s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1nh v\u00e1c nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 ghi b\u00e0n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Laurent Koscielny?</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Wolvehampton muon mua Vida\" title=\"Wolvehampton mu\u1ed1n mua Vida\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/4/tan-binh-ngoai-hang-anh-muon-gianh-hang-hot-world-cup-voi-arsenal-va-liverpool.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arsenal mu\u1ed1n mua Vida</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal mu\u1ed1n mua Domagoj Vida c\u1ee7a Besiktas thay th\u1ebf Laurent Koscielny, ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea chi 89 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Courtois</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Jan Oblak c\u1ee7a Atletico Madrid thay Thibaut Courtois, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi 89 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Madrid.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>MU ch\u1ed1t 120 tri\u1ec7u euro cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Pogba</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU mua Milinkovic-Savic c\u1ee7a Lazio trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Paul Pogba chia tay s\u00e2n Old Trafford, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf tin t\u01b0\u1edfng r\u1eb1ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd gi\u00fap h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Atletico \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o m\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Atletico Madrid mua Nikola Kalinic th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao, theo Gianluca Di Marzio \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Madrid s\u1eafp c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb AC Milan.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Courtois t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn Real b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thibaut Courtois mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Chelsea t\u1edbi Real Madrid, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Chelsea trong khi Hazard,&nbsp;Giroud v\u00e0 Kante \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>MU \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Alderweireld</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Toby Alderweireld\" title=\"Toby Alderweireld\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/5-thuong-vu-co-the-xay-ra-truoc-khi-ttcn-tai-anh-dong-cua.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU s\u1eafp c\u00f3 Toby Alderweireld</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Toby Alderweireld c\u1ee7a Tottenham, th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 khi Tottenham mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trung v\u1ec7 thay th\u1ebf.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Real Madrid nh\u1eafm sao Juventus thay th\u1ebf Modric</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Miralem Pjanic thay Luka Modric, Los Blancos ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 70 tri\u1ec7u euro mua ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Juventus.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5179","checkdouble":"193907"},{"date":"08:39 07/08","title":"Arsenal nh\u1eadn tin bu\u1ed3n khi theo \u0111u\u1ed5i sao ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh AC Milan","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/7/ac-milan-khuoc-tu-loi-de-nghi-cua-arsenal-cho-ricardo-rodriguez.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Italia, AC Milan \u0111\u00e3 kh\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Arsenal d\u00e0nh cho h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh Ricardo Rodriguez.</h2><h2>Arsenal nh\u1eadn tin bu\u1ed3n t\u1eeb Milan</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Unai Emery \u0111ang \u01b0u ti\u00ean chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 m\u1ed9t h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y. Sead Kolasinac s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u 10 tu\u1ea7n v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1edbi g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i t\u1eeb tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u1edbi Chelsea.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNacho Monreal c\u0169ng ch\u01b0a k\u1ecbp h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c. V\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn Arsenal thi\u1ebfu \u0111i m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nArsenal s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Man City ngay trong ng\u00e0y khai m\u00e0n Premier League. V\u00e0 v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, HLV Emery ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n duy nh\u1ea5t \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb Ainsley Maitland-Niles.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Milan kh\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Arsenal cho h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Ricardo Rodriguez h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Milan kh\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Arsenal cho h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Ricardo Rodriguez h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/ac-milan-khuoc-tu-loi-de-nghi-cua-arsenal-cho-ricardo-rodriguez.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Arsenal nh\u1eadn tin bu\u1ed3n v\u1ee5 Rodriguez</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo t\u1edd Corriere dello Sport, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/arsenal-nham-sao-thuy-sy-thay-nacho-monreal-172-193853.html\" target=\"_blank\">Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb cho Ricardo Rodriguez</span> c\u1ee7a AC Milan. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Milano \u0111\u00e3 kh\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 kho\u1ea3ng 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a Rodriguez r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n San Siro. Nh\u01b0ng tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, Arsenal c\u0169ng g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1ec1 th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u0103m nay, th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i Anh s\u1ebd \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda s\u1edbm h\u01a1n th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ec7. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, h\u1ea1n ch\u00f3t \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 t\u00e2n binh l\u00e0 v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 N\u0103m, tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m Man United thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n v\u1edbi Leicester t\u1ea1i Old Trafford.</div>\r\n<h2>Milan quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Rodriguez</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hi\u1ec7n ch\u01b0a r\u00f5 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 Arsenal chi ra \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c AC Milan nh\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi. Nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y l\u00e0 Rossoneri c\u0169ng ch\u01b0a mu\u1ed1n chia tay tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Th\u1ee5y S\u0128 v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 cho d\u00f9 Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 g\u1eedi th\u00eam nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb th\u00ec h\u1ecd c\u0169ng s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn th\u00eam tin bu\u1ed3n. B\u1edfi ph\u00eda Milan \u0111ang r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u00e0 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i top 4.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nRicardo Rodriguez \u0111\u00e3 gia nh\u1eadp s\u00e2n San Siro t\u1eeb Wolfsburg m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i v\u00e0 c\u00f3 47 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 Milan \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng nh\u01b0ng Rodriguez v\u1eabn ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00f2ng tin t\u1eeb c\u00e1c fan b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Arsenal:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-da-tim-duoc-nguoi-thay-the-laurent-koscielny-172-193898.html\">Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Laurent Koscielny?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-gia-nhap-cuoc-dua-gianh-boateng-voi-mu-172-193871.html\">Arsenal gia nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh sao tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1edbi M.U</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5178","checkdouble":"193914"}]}